  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK201">
<l>tīviṉaiya rañcā viḻumiyā rañcuvar</l>
<l> tīviṉai yeṉṉuñ cerukku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who have experience of evil deeds will not fear, but the excellent will fear the pride of sin.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
